window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>A new steamy AGE GAP Bodyguard Irish Mafia STANDALONE</i></b></p> <p>Eriu Quinn is off-limits.<br> Too young. Too innocent. And far too forbidden.</p> <p>Her father is the head of the Irish Mob.<br> And I'm just her bodyguard tasked to keep her safe.</p> <p>She's my job, but she's also a maddening temptation. <br> One I need to stay away from.</p> <p>But I underestimate that feisty little spitfire.<br> She creeps under my skin.<br> Pushes all of my buttons.<br> Until I unravel...<br> <br> I can’t resist the untouched Irish princess.<br> <br> With every hungered look, with every illicit touch, I want her more.<br> Downright needing her, until the lines start to blur.</p> <p>But I can't have her.</p> <p>She has no idea who I truly am.<br> My past is as dark as it is dangerous.<br> <br> And my enemies are coming.</p> <p>If she’s mine,<br> they’ll come for her too.</p> <p>When her life is threatened,<br> I have no choice but to save her.</p> <p>Though saving her comes at a price.</p> <p><b><i>Ruthless Savage</i></b><i> is a standalone age gap mafia, bodyguard, grumpy/sunshine romance with a feisty heroine, and a possessive, touch her &amp; I'll unalive you type of hero. It contains a HEA.</i></p>"; 
